The <strong><code>color</code></strong> CSS property sets the foreground <a href="/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/color_value">color value</a> of an element's text and <a href="/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/text-decoration">text decorations</a>, and sets the <a href="/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/currentcolor" title="REDIRECT https://developer.mozilla.org/docs/Web/CSS/color_value#currentColor"><code>currentcolor</code></a> value.